uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.jdbc.filter

Class NegatingFilterVisitor<T extends DataObject>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.jdbc.filter.NegatingFilterVisitor<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of filter
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    FilterVisitor<BaseFilter<T>,T>

    public class NegatingFilterVisitor<T extends DataObject>
extends java.lang.Object
implements FilterVisitor<BaseFilter<T>,T>
    A FilterVisitor that negates the selection of filter. Ordering information is not preserved.
